Memory upgrade - 800 MHz not 667 MHz
Great Netbook!<br /><br />Careful with the memory upgrade.  The 667 MHz 2GB module mentioned on this page is not suitable for the 1005PE - mine kept freezing.  Instead, order the 800 MHz module, Amazon # (ASIN): B001342KM8
      
