After reading reviews etc. we decided to replace our current Eureka with this one.  Ours quit running because we did not really keep up with maintenance.  We have had it for 7+ years and like it.  I like that this one has the Paw attachment for the stairs.  It is a little heavy and noisy, but it cleans great.  This is a great vacuum for the money.
      
