Xbox holiday bundle...pure/lego batman
I am a long time user of XBOX products. I've owned Sony products. And to me, They just don't make the cut. The newer xbox's (This one included) Have a new chip in them...Code named "Jasper". And what this chip does, Is it runs at a lower and cooler point. Thus putting your risk for a hardware failure (ex: RROD) very low. Xbox has always had the best graphics, And best live and gaming expierience, In my opinion. I have red ringed one xbox. and that was one of the first models that came out. Since early 07, I have had no problems. I have never played Lego batman, But it seems like it has a pretty cool co-op mode for children, Pure is a different story, Pure is a great game for all ages. It takes strategy, Yet it's easy for anyone to play. You can design and customize your own ATV's, Race them, Jump them, Trick them. Anything really. The graphics are great, And I have expierienced no lag with the game (outside of XBOXLIVE) The elite comes with a few cool features, A huge hard drive, Store your music, Videos, Games. Sleek look. And a matching controller and headset. Streaming videos on XLIVE is easy with netflix. It's very convienient, And easy to use. Xbox Live doesn't cost much money, I spend 40 dollars for a year, And I play just about every day. It's well worth it. I personally use an xbox wireless adapter for game play. It works amazingly, I'm all the way across the house of a 3500 sq house, And I still get a strong signal. If you want good game play for all ages, Quality systems. And good game choices, Choose XBOX. and Keep your eye out for Call of duty: Modern Warfare 2. Releasing November 10th, 2009. Game looks AMAZING! NOTE: ALL XBOX CONSOLES COME WITH A 3 YEAR RED RING OF DEATH WARRANTY, AND A 1 YEAR WARRANTY FOR ALL OTHER XBOX RELATED ISSUES. BUY WITH CONFIDENCE.
      
