 [...] bucks (Half life 2, HL2 episode 1, HL2 episode 2, Portal (same physics engine as half life, and an absolutely amazing game to get the mind juices flowing), team fortress (an online game)). Be sure to read the manual at least once if you are a new user and follow guidelines on optimum placement to avoid overheating and dust issues (like never put the console, or any cooling fan accessory base directly on a carpet or other porous material that could pick up dust and push it into the console)<br /><br />Overall, I am very happy with this product, the shipping, and accessories that I got/bought with it.
      
