Got Pink? 360 controller
If you've got an Xbox 360, you need controllers.  This pink one is perfect if you are comfortable in your masculinity, or if your favorite color is pink.  If you want to make this controller a bit more manly, take a black marker and draw a skull or two on it.<br /><br />The layout of the buttons on the Xbox 360 is amazing.  It's perfect for many of the games that are on the 360.  The rumble is effective, and the wireless capacity is wonderful.<br /><br />The only beef I have, is that I've had two controllers that become loose on the left analog stick, and they began to drag the cursor when not touched.  The Xbox Warranty I had from the console replaced them free of charge.  Luckily I had extra controllers to get me by in the week it took to replace it.<br /><br />When matched with the rechargable battery pack, they give you lots of gaming time between charges.
      
