It's like playing war as a kid - with all the best weapons!!!
Could not recommend a game more.  Amazing detail in every regard.  The game grows with you.  (I have logged well over 100 hours and am still loving it). <br /><br />Quick review of all three sections...<br /><br />Training/Challenges - "Special Ops" - section definitely helps hone the skills and learn the weapons.  AI is very challenging.<br /><br />Career - fun story line - great play and graphics. You'll want to finish all three levels (unlike many other similar games).  Again, AI is very challenging.<br /><br />Live - clearly the most fun.  I play the "team deathmatch" - you increase your rank throughout the process and play with "like" players.  5-10 minute challenges that play 6 on 6.  It literally is likely playing war as a kid with all the real strategy, thought and action required to do well - let your imagination run wild and it still wont describe how detailed and fun this is.  I have not played the other challenges as I am addicted to deathmatch express.
      
