More to Love!
Who thought that you could improve on one of the best selling fps games ever? The maps and weapons are beautifully detailed, infinity ward has outdone themselves. While single player was a bit of a disappointment, multi player was vastly improved. There are so many new guns, attachments, equipment, and perks to make pro. To all considering it, BUY IT! Without a doubt the best fps shooter at the moment. I can't wait for MW3! However, Treyarch has been a disappointment to the call of duty name. Infinity ward should be given full rites.
      
