Most Amazing Game Ever Made
PlayStation 3 has had some pretty amazing games this generation, however, nothing could have prepared me for the greatness that is God of War 3. The graphics, sense of scale, no load times, framerate that never bogs down, and fluidity of combat never ceases to amaze me. The weapons you ungraciously rip from other bosses' cold, dead hands are all a blast to use, a couple of personal favorites being the Claws of Hades and the Nemean Cestus. The items are are fun to use, and recharge with their own meter, so you don't have to limit their use. The magic attacks are weapon specific and appropriately epic and effective. <br />Epic. That is an appropriate word to sum up this gem of a game from Sony Santa Monica. This is easily the best game this generation so far, with uncharted 2 coming in a (close) second.<br />If you have any doubts about this game, do yourself a favor and play it. Let me know how you feel after the cronos fight. I'm pretty sure you will agree.
      
