My Wii Excerise
The Wii Sports Resort is a great set of games.  I originally played this game at a relatives home and instantly fell in love with it.  I have some mobility issues and when I tried out some of these games I realized I was able to get up and move around without a ton of effort, and all the while I was having a blast.  I went home and bought myself a Wii system shortly after that and this was the first game I sought to buy.  Mainly because it has several games within the one.  I love playing all of the games, they are great fun.  I've heard some people complain about the graphics and although I somewhat agree that in this age of technology you would think the graphics would be more advanced but for a video game I think you can adjust to it.  It does take a couple of rounds of any one of the games to get the feel for the controler in that particular game but once you play them a bit you'll get the feel for each one.  <br /><br />This game is well worth it's price because it gives you several games within it to keep you busy for hours.  I give it a solid thumbs up!
      
