Makes the Wii a better gaming system
This piece of equipment makes the Wii about 300% more responsive. The reviews based on price are just absurd. The reviews are SUPPOSED to be based on the product. As for the guy complaining about the responsiveness with Tennis? I can't speak to that, but Tiger Woods golf is a phenomenally better experience with the Motion plus.
      
