Great game of course
I really enjoy the game however I strongly recommend not bothering getting the wheels for the game.  Both my wife and I felt that sometimes when we were using the wheel it didn't register all our turn inputs properly.  We prefer using just the nun chuck and the Wii mote.  So just a heads up if you were planning on getting the wheels for the game.
      
