Favorite Video Game Of All Time
Mario Cart Wii is the next version of one of Nintendo's most successful and iconic video games, but this version takes the game to a whole new level. In addition to improved graphics, more tracks, and more character options (including your Mii), this game also allows online play. Friends can meet up and set up a "private room" where they race each other, or you can race with players around the world. I have enjoyed this feature the most. Every Tuesday night I meet up with 12 friends to race each other and it's a blast to knock your best friend off their cart so you can win the race. Very Fun!<br /><br />I can't recommend this game enough for any Nintendo Wii owner. Sure the basic concept of Mario Cart is still the same, but the enhancements for the Wii version make it worth the price. Although the Wii Wheel is not required to play the game I think it's worth the extra few dollars for the fun of it.
      
