What you wanted in Wii Fit the first time
Wii Fit Plus lets you create a custom Yoga/Strength workout routine - placing all your favorite workouts in a menu so there's no stopping after each one to select a new workout. <br /><br />Importing your Wii Fit profiles works as expected - we had 6 and they all transferred fine. Wii Fit Plus lets you add baby and pet profiles - not useful, but cute.<br /><br />I just got it yesterday so I've only played the skateboard game, but they look fun, worth the $20 just for those. <br /><br />There's small mental challenges, like after you run, it asks if you remember seeing certain things, and a balance test has you only move if the number is 4 or less. Not hard, but requires a tiny bit more thought.<br /><br />Definitely a good purchase. I just wish they'd done this stuff originally!
      
