Wii Fit Plus is Awesome!
WII FIT PLUS FEATURES:<br /><br />OBSTACLE COURSE - This is a fun, simple game which reminds me of Mario games.. but you're actually Mario! You get to run around, jump, dodge obstacles and make it through new stages.<br /><br />RHYTHM KUNG-FU - I love this one! It's fun and you get to do kung fu with a beat. You have to do it on time and you get to do different poses and punches.<br /><br />SKATEBOARD ARENA - This is a great game, because you get to skateboard! You get to jump and push off the wii board do tricks on the half-pipes. Very realistic!<br /><br />BIRD'S EYE BULL'S EYE - I love this game! haha, it's funny because you're the flying chicken and you have to flap onto the targets! Great excercising because you have to work to flap!<br /><br />SEGWAY CIRCUIT - This isn't really excercising but it's fun because you get to drive around in a little scooter and pop balloons, but you have to beware of the moles!<br /><br />BASIC RUN PLUS - This is better than the basic run because you get to take different paths following different cats. Also, you get to take a quiz on what you observed such as maybe a mario icon, or how many cats were running past you.<br /><br />RHYTHM PARADE - Wow, this is quite fun... it's like you are actually in a parade and you have to have great timing with this.<br /><br />SNOWBALL FIGHT - Not as much action as I expected, and not as fun.. it's like a first person shooter game where you shoot the people.. not the best.<br /><br />DRIVING RANGE - This is a different approach to golf, where you don't just hit the ball. You learn how to shift your weight and get to practice and nearing the center hole. It's a great way to learn how to place and swing.<br /><br />PERFECT 10 - Haha this is fun.. you need some small math abilities, unless you don't know what numbers add up to 10 then this is not the game for you.. it's fun because you get to swing your hips from side to side and add up to 10. Great game!<br /><br />ISLAND CYCLING - This is like biking, but you're stepping on the wii fit board. It's cool because you can accelerate and you have to collect flags.<br /><br />TILT CITY - This game you need to build coordination, because you have to tilt the wii remote differently than the wii fit board to get the balls into the cups to create fireworks! Pretty fun!<br /><br />TABLE TILT PLUS - Great addition to the table tilt game on the regular wii fit. Trying to get the balls in the holes is much tougher now.<br /><br />BALANCE BUBBLE PLUS - Much harder than balance bubble, but a great challenge because you have to make it through in the dark! Haha.<br /><br />BIG TOP JUGGLING - Not my favorite because it's kind of difficult, but my sister likes it and you have to balance/shift your weight while juggling balls.<br /><br />EXERCISES:<br /><br />3 New Yoga Exercises for Advanced Users.<br />3 New Strength Exercises for Advanced Users. <br /><br />Wii Fit Plus: Tracks how many calories you burned, and you can make your own routines. This way you don't have to keep restarting. Also, it can weigh your pets and has already set routines for your hips or maybe your arms. They also have new body tests, and it is a great addition to your wii.
      
