atteries, 1 in the psp while the other charging. Another is having 2 psps but highly unlikely if you don't have the money. But after seeing the PSP Go, you might want to buy a backup PSP 3000.<br /><br />What seperates this from the Nintendo DS? Much cooler graphics & a bigger screen. And you can watch movies. You can even download them.
      
