Top-notch reproduction
I have always wondered what a two hundred dollar pair of earbuds would sound like, but now I don't care.  These J3s are incredible.  It takes more volume to power them than other buds (moderate volume is close to max volume on my Archos 5) but the sound is startling.  The bass is tight and defined.  If it is on the recording, you will hear it.  The highs are more crisp and clear than any other earbud I have tried.  I simply haven't heard music with this much clarity in years.  If you like muddy, booming bass that probably wasn't on the recording, you won't like these.  If you like the full range and every nuance, buy them!<br />And don't even try to listen to them until you've broken them in at their website!  This is more of a necessity than any other earbuds I've owned.
      
