Most awesome and LEGEN.... wait for it ... DARY speakers
The Harman/Kardon SountSticks It is great in every way - from physical appearance to to clear, crispy sound. They provide a full sound range - from the lows to the mids and the highs. Every song I tested it with contains the majority of the details I would hear when listening through in-ear earphones. The sound of instrumental music sounds fantastic with these speakers. The sound of acoustic guitar is very clear - as clear as the speakers itself. <br /><br />Its appearance is very attractive. I even wanted to attach it to the ceiling as my room light bulb. The blue light in the speakers looks holographic and gives the speakers its uniqueness. I wish that Harman Kardon could attach those blue LED light bulbs on those satellites. It would look really awesome with them. <br /><br />As a precaution to future buyers: If you live in a multi-floor apartment or have neighbors, I would recommend doing some homework on sound-absorption materials. The subwoofer produces very strong bass that I could even hear it from inside my bathroom about 40 feet away! My neighbor has complained to me very often that she could not sleep because of them. I had to find ways to absorb some of the bass before they reached the first level. Aside from that, this speaker is the one I would recommend to people who love to listen to music, play games, or watch movies from their computer or their home theater system.<br /><br />There's no consumer speakers that would sound as great as this at this price. It's worth each and every single penny you pay.
      
