Beware of the Flashy Aluminum Bottles
Need a bottle of water with you all the time? Has all the news about BPA leaching into your water from plastic water bottles got you paranoid? Feel like you need to do your part to save the Earth by not buying bottled water?  Klean Kanteen has got you covered! <br /><br />Personally, I have the 27 ounce model with both the loop cap and a sports cap (Klean Kanteen Sports Cap). The loop cap is great for everyday use i.e., around the office, and the I use the sport cap at the gym and when I go biking (the 27 ounce bottle fits into standard water bottle cages on bikes).<br /><br />If you are a BPA-phobe, like me, beware of aluminum water bottles (e.g., <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B000RI4ES4">Sigg Lifestyle Loop Top Water Bottle (1.0-Liters)</a>) which use a coating/liner that may or may contain BPA.  Stick with stainless steel.  You can't go wrong with a Klean Kanteen. I have already converted/scared/guilted a few people at my office from plastic bottles to Klean Kanteens and they are all happy with the switch.
      
