short women aren't the only people who clean!  My 5'10" self and my 6'3" husband both have to hunch over to mop the floor with this.  It'd be lovely if the handle could extend.<br /><br />- Doesn't do a great job on grout - but nothing does.  I've decided I just hate tile and grout period.<br /><br />- It does take some effort to push, but cleans overall more quickly than the Powered Floormate.<br /><br />- Like any machine it can't get right up close to the walls and though it's mophead fits under the cabinets, it simply cannot clean right in the crack where the floor meets.  So every so often I have to get down and hand scrub those areas.<br /><br />----<br /><br />Highly, highly recommend for regular use.  Does a great job at steaming the dried on grime and gunk my kids regularly paste the house with.  <br /><br />
      
