GREAT PRINTER - FIREWALL PROBLEM
This is a truly wonderful product! But the software can get corrupted or have conflicts and this can cause many hours of woe.<br /><br />Here is a fix to prevent others from going insane: if you are using Zone Alarm and you find yourself unable to print anything from your computer - disable Zone Alarm for 5 seconds and try to print - whether you are successful or not - start Zone Alarm up again. After I printed successfully and started up Zone Alarm again I was still able to print. I run Windows XP Pro.<br /><br />I hope this helps someone else!
      
