Excellent Family Tent
I recently purchased this tent for the Memorial Day weekend and had it shipped over night. I had it two days after ordering. The tent is very spacious and has alot of features. There are two doors which are very useful. The windows are over-sized which provide plenty of air flow. The rain fly worked excellent on the last night when it rained all night. There were no leakes at all! The rain fly has a built in canapoy which works well during the rain also. There is also a removeable dividing wall that is very easy to use. There is no built in tarp on the floor of the tent like in other models I have seen. I used a tarp for the ground underneath and it worked well. The set up was extremely easy my wife and I had it up in less than 30 minutes. I would recomend this tent to any one who wants an excellent product at a reasonable price.
      
