Trainer is excellent.  First off, it's $80 so you can't expect the best piece of equipment on the market.  Second, for those reviewers that felt the quick release hub was required... it's not! The standard (non-quickrelease) axle on by bicycle fits just fine. In fact, I use this trainer daily with my road bike and have zero ZERO Z E R O  complaints. <br /><br />As far as coming fully assembled, I took it out of the box, sat it on the floor, positioned the bike and tightened the axle holders until it was tight enough to hold the bike safely.  Can't get much easier than that! <br /><br />Love it.  Recommend it whole-heartedly!
      
